videos.description: Emmitt Williams gets the ball at the free throw line and aggressively drives to the rim through contact for the hoop and the harm.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (LSU's Williams muscles in for and-1 bucket) 2020/02/01

videos.headline: LSU's Williams muscles in for and-1 bucket

videos.description: In the closing seconds of the first half, Austin Crowley hoists up a contested jumper and banks it home off the backboard to beat the buzzer for Ole Miss.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Ole Miss banks in jumper at the horn) 2020/02/01

videos.headline: Ole Miss banks in jumper at the horn

videos.description: Ole Miss' Devontae Shuler corrals a loose ball, crosses up a defender and finishes in the paint with a double-clutch layup in traffic.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Shuler weaves through defense for acrobatic lay-in) 2020/02/01

videos.headline: Shuler weaves through defense for acrobatic lay-in

videos.description: After Javonte Smart's missed layup in transition, both Marlon Taylor and Trendon Watford crash the offensive glass for the simultaneous putback slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (2 LSU players stuff putback dunk at same time) 2020/02/01

videos.headline: 2 LSU players stuff putback dunk at same time

videos.description: LSU's Javonte Smart throws his inbounds pass off Carlos Curry's back and quickly grabs the ball back to score the and-1 bucket.
